just one sip away from the perfect 𝓮𝓼𝓬𝓪𝓹𝓮 this summer w/ @7brewcoffee’s new drink lineup! 🌺😎

drinks i ordered: 
🍋‍🟩: Key Lime Pie Lemon Freeze! 
* flavors- lime, lemon, & white chocolate!
- if you know me, then you know that key lime pie is my fave dessert; so i knew i had to try this one off the summer menu! this drink honestly tasted like key lime pie in a cup! it was absolutely so delicious & i will be back to grab another one before summer ends! 🙌🏼😋
🍉: Pink Paradise Lemonade
* flavors- cherry, watermelon, & raspberry!
- as a lover of fruit drink refreshers, i knew this one would be a great option for me to try as well! it was so refreshing & perfectly balanced. & who doesn’t love an ice cold lemonade on a hot summer day! highly recommend! ☀️🥤🍒

let me know below if you would try either one of these summer drinks!! 🤩
